OL,3,CCumberland set to see maximum council
OL,4,Ctax increase
OL,6,FCouncil tax in Cumberland is expected
OL,7,Fto rise by the maximum 4.99% in the
OL,8,Fupcoming local authority budget.
OL,10,FAt a meeting on 17 February Cumberland
OL,11,FCouncil's executive recommended the
OL,12,F4.99% increase.
OL,14,FCouncils in England can only raise tax
OL,15,Fby 5% or more if they hold a
OL,16,Freferendum.
