OL,6,FThe proposed budget includes #371m for
OL,7,Fessential services such as bin
OL,8,Fcollections, adult social care and
OL,9,Froad repairs, along with #280m
OL,10,Fspending on the council's buildings
OL,11,Fand local communities.
OL,13,FWhat would a 4.99% increase cost
OL,14,Fhouseholds?
OL,16,FThe authority said since its creation
OL,17,Fin 2023, it has already saved #55m.
