OL,3,CCumberland set to see maximum council
OL,4,Ctax increase
OL,6,FIt comes as Cumberland Council's
OL,7,Fconsultation inviting residents and
OL,8,Fbusinesses to share their views on
OL,9,Fproposals for the 2026/27 budget has
OL,10,Fnow closed.
OL,12,FCllr Barbara Cannon said: "Our
OL,13,Ffinancial situation remains
OL,14,Fchallenging as demand for some
OL,15,Fservices continues to rise at a rate
OL,16,Ffaster than funding.
