OL,3,CCumberland set to see maximum council
OL,4,Ctax increase
OL,6,F"Council tax provides the lion's share
OL,7,Fof our funding, and this will only
OL,8,Fincrease over the next three years.
OL,9,FTherefore, any decision not to
OL,10,Fincrease council tax, even if just by
OL,11,Finflation, would have a major impact
OL,12,Fon our ability to deliver services in
OL,13,Fthe future.
OL,15,F"We are very aware of the implications
OL,16,Fof increasing council tax given the
OL,17,Fongoing cost of living issues for
OL,18,Flocal residents.
