OL,6,F"This is why we offer a very generous
OL,7,FCouncil Tax Reduction Scheme which
OL,8,Fcosts around #22m a year, and can help
OL,9,Freduce the bill of those on low
OL,10,Fincomes. I'd encourage anyone who
OL,11,Fthinks they are eligible but has yet
OL,12,Fto apply to contact us."
OL,14,FThe final budget is expected to be
OL,15,Fagreed on 3 March.
